name: The Dream-carvers
description:
For the Dream-carvers, true beauty lies in the eternal and immutable.
Their wonderful sculptures lie far and wide across the Tapestry, the result of their endless quest for still perfection.
Those who come across their works are invaded by feelings of awe and reverence, for their gift for sculpting is second to none.
Their dreamer sculptures, in particular, seem to have a life of their own.
